articles.title: Gypsy Rose Blanchard on life outside of prison: 'They want a perfect victim' - Good Morning America
articles.description: Blanchard also discussed the "hate" she says she's received since her release from prison.
articles.content:
Gypsy Rose Blanchard is speaking out about her life months after being released from prison, where she served time for the murder of her mother, Clauddinnea "Dee Dee" Blanchard, in 2015.
